  "Description": {
    "English": "Shifting nanite clusters sewn together with a <span class=\"name name-special\">pugneum filament</span>, this circuit is painfully hot to the touch. The purple light that leaks from within its wiring has softened, as if it has become less hostile.<br><br>Previously embedded within a Sentinel Walker, this semi-organic computer has been altered by both <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Iteration: Tethys</span> and a <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Messenger of the Atlas</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "这块电路是通过<span class=\"name name-special\">普茵单纤维</span>连接的纳米星团，摸上去很烫手。线路深处漏出的邪恶紫光已变得柔和，敌意也似乎没有之前那么强烈了。<br><br>原本是一台护卫步行机的内部构件，<span class=\"name name-stellar\">迭代：特提斯</span>与一名<span class=\"name name-fuel\">阿特拉斯的信使</span>已经对这块半有机电脑进行了改造。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "這塊電路板用<span class=\"name name-special\">搏絲</span>將會變形的奈米機群縫在一起，非常燙且難以觸碰。從其線路中滲透出來的紫色燈光已經減弱，看起來敵意降低許多。<br><br>原本內嵌於巡警步行機中，這台半有機電腦已經被<span class=\"name name-stellar\">迭代：忒堤斯</span>及<span class=\"name name-fuel\">寰宇的使者</span>修改過。"
  },
