  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Each day, Iteration: Tethys can provide a <span class=\"name name-special\">Radiant Brain</span> in exchange for a <span class=\"name name-special\">Walker Brain</span>.<br>Meet with Tethys aboard the Space Anomaly.<br>In space, summon the <span class=\"name name-special\">Anomaly</span> from the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "每一天，迭代：特提斯都会提供一个<span class=\"name name-special\">闪光大脑</span>以换取<span class=\"name name-special\">步行机大脑</span>。<br>与特提斯在太空异象上见面。<br>在快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）中召唤<span class=\"name name-special\">太空异象</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "迭代：忒堤斯每天可以提供一個<span class=\"name name-special\">光芒閃耀的腦</span>，來交換一個<span class=\"name name-special\">步行機腦</span>。<br>登上太空異常和忒堤斯碰面。<br>身處太空時，你可以從快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 叫出<span class=\"name name-special\">異常</span>。"
